<p>Like, ahem, people of a certain mind-type, what I watch to tune
out has often been of people assembling, disassembling, or making
things. I’ve collected a good range of those and here they are:
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVqhLG8wo5k" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Baumgartner Restoration</a>
